Launch using the launch file joystickRemap.launch 

Launch File Parameters:

gps_file_pathname:
Specify a gpsFile from which it reads gps coordinates. 
The gps coordinates should be in the meters as converted by the gpsProjection library provided.

Format of the gps file: 
0 1234.000 24534.000 0 
1 4343.000 3423.000 0
0 3423.000 32532.000 0
2 

0 denotes obstacle. 1 denotes target. 2 signals the end of the file (these are tags)

each value is seperated by a space. the format is:

tag gpsX gpsY 0

velocity_sub_topic:
topic where the control commands are published (the base velocity control commands) 

velocity_pub_topic:
topic to publish the commands to (this should be the one to make the landshark move) 

use_dw_monitor:

status_msgs_topic:
topic name to publish to that says true/false if the monitor is running or not

